Created when a bounded unit of work ships. Template at `docs/templates/slice-outcome.md` (Pass 3f). Frontmatter: `slice_id`, `title`, `date_shipped`, `status` (shipped/reverted/partial), `related_risks`, `related_findings`, `related_adrs`. Body sections: Goal, What shipped, Verification (table), Findings surfaced, Decisions deferred, Cross-links. After shipping: add the slice to the phase's roadmap entry (per workflows.md; this is the step that has been missed for 1c.3-A through 1c.3-E — see Q17).

